==製作==
2013年10月31日，宣布[[麥可·法斯賓達|麥可·法斯賓達]]將於犯罪片《犯罪教條》中主演，為{{le|亞當·史密斯 (導演)|Adam Smith (director)|亞當·史密斯}}執導、亞歷斯塔·席登斯負責撰寫劇本<ref name=FassbenderCast>{{cite news|last1=Kemp|first1=Stuart|title=AFM: Michael Fassbender in Talks to Star in 'Trespass Against Us'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/afm-michael-fassbender-talks-star-652130|accessdate=2015-05-08|work=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2013-10-31|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111192220/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/afm-michael-fassbender-talks-star-652130|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影由Protagonist Pictures製作，而席登斯、蓋兒·艾根及{{le|安德烈·卡爾德伍德|Andrea Calderwood}}則將擔任監製<ref name="FassbenderCast" />。{{le|Film4製片公司|Film4 Productions}}將共同為電影出資，其配樂由[[化學兄弟|化學兄弟]]負責<ref name="FassbenderCast" />。2014年5月16日，演員[[布蘭頓·葛利森|布蘭頓·葛利森]]、{{le|西恩·哈里斯|Sean Harris}}、{{le|琳賽·馬歇爾|Lyndsey Marshal}}、[[羅里·金尼爾|羅里·金尼爾]]和{{le|基利安·史考特|Killian Scott}}都已簽約參演<ref name="Variety" />。2014年6月，電影於英國開始正式拍攝<ref>{{cite news|title=Ezra Khan films Trespass Against Us|url=http://www.sainou.com/ezra-khan-films-trespass-us/|accessdate=2015-05-08|work=sainou.com|date=2014-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518071735/http://www.sainou.com/ezra-khan-films-trespass-us/|archive-date=2015-05-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==發行==
2014年5月16日，[[獅門影視公司|獅門]]獲得了電影的英國發行權<ref name=Variety>{{cite news|last1=Barraclough|first1=Leo|title=Cannes: Lionsgate Acquires U.K. Rights to Michael Fassbender Film ‘Trespass Against Us’|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/markets-festivals/cannes-lionsgate-acquires-u-k-rights-to-michael-fassbender-film-trespass-against-us-1201183386/|accessdate=2015-05-08|work=variety.com|date=2014-05-16|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424223448/http://variety.com/2014/film/markets-festivals/cannes-lionsgate-acquires-u-k-rights-to-michael-fassbender-film-trespass-against-us-1201183386/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而[[A24_(公司)|A24]]則於2014年12月16日獲得了電影的美國發行權<ref>{{cite news|last1=Jaafar|first1=Ali|title=‘Trespass Against Us’ Finds Home With A24|url=http://deadline.com/2014/12/trespass-against-us-a24-michael-fassbender-brendan-gleeson-1201327048/|accessdate=2015-05-08|work=deadline.com|date=2014-12-16|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211193229/https://deadline.com/2014/12/trespass-against-us-a24-michael-fassbender-brendan-gleeson-1201327048/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《犯罪教條》定於2016年11月24日以[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]（VOD）方式發行，並於2017年1月20日在美國[[有限上映|有限上映]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/trailers/769125-trespass-against-us-trailer|title=Trespass Against Us Trailer and Poster Featuring Michael Fassbender|website=ComingSoon.net|first=Max|last=Evry|date=2016-09-22|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108124537/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/trailers/769125-trespass-against-us-trailer|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://thefilmstage.com/reviews/tiff-review-trespass-against-us/|title=Trespass Against Us TIFF 2016 Review|website=The Film Stage|first=Christopher|last=Schobert|date=2016-09-10|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2017-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128224422/https://thefilmstage.com/reviews/tiff-review-trespass-against-us/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影於2017年3月3日在英國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.launchingfilms.com/release-schedule|title=Tresspass Against Us|website=Launching Films|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223095941/http://www.launchingfilms.com/release-schedule|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在此前，電影最初於2016年9月9日在[[2016年多倫多國際影展|2016年多倫多國際影展]]上作首映。

===評價===
《犯罪教條》獲得了褒貶不一的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於61條評論，新鮮度57%，平均得分5.5／10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trespass_against_us_2016/|title=Tresspass Against Us|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810185400/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trespass_against_us_2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，基於16條評論，獲得了50分的中等評價<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/trespass-against-us|title=Tresspass Against Us|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905060714/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/trespass-against-us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

